** TextFlow **
Enables multi-field text using TextFields for applications like multicolumn text and flowing text around an image. Multiple versions with different capabilities.

TextFlowLite - basic text flow capability

TextFlow - adds support for widows / orphans and overflow text.

TextFlowPro - supports selection and editing with some limitations (ex. right click editing menu works improperly).

ex.
var tf:TextFlow = new TextFlow([textField1, textField2, textField3]);